Piggy o'l fellow taverntavernnC0none764493876searchvar1.15892******03*Following its name, this establishment is reputed for its ham stew. All kinds of people hang out in here; bandits are a rare meat since a lot of royal guards come to eat regularly. The tavern keeper, Piggy, will be a good friend, especially if you pay him your food and drinks the same day you order it.